<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 08:09:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>飞行者因在湍流中喝“滚烫”茶而严重烧伤，起诉捷蓝航空</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/flyer-suffers-severe-burns-due-to-scalding-hot-tea-served-amid-turbulence-sues-jetblue/articleshow/111654337.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111654337.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔贾娜·刘易斯 (Tahjana Lewis) 在 5 月 15 日的一次航班颠簸期间因被提供的“滚烫”茶严重烧伤而起诉捷蓝航空，索赔 150 万美元。投诉强调了严重疏忽，指出茶的温度很危险，而且船员的帮助不足。刘易斯经历了严重烧伤和情绪困扰，影响了她的工作能力和女儿的健康。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 07:12:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/flyer-suffers-severe-burns-due-to-scalding-hot-tea-served-amid-turbulence-sues-jetblue/articleshow/111654337.cms</guid></item><item><title>北约指责中国“促成”乌克兰战争；波兰附近的“反恐”军事演习加剧了人们的担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/nato-accuses-china-of-enabling-ukraine-war-antiterrorist-military-drills-near-poland-heighten-concerns/articleshow/111652560.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111652560.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在华盛顿举行的北约峰会上，盟国承诺向乌克兰提供 F-16 喷气式飞机，并承诺未来可能为基辅提供会员资格。中国因援助俄罗斯而受到批评，并担心其核能力和太空能力。盟友敦促中国停止支持俄罗斯。与此同时，中国与白俄罗斯在波兰边境附近举行演习，加剧了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 06:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/nato-accuses-china-of-enabling-ukraine-war-antiterrorist-military-drills-near-poland-heighten-concerns/articleshow/111652560.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示，对他的压力来自精英阶层。选民描绘了一幅更加复杂的图景</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-says-pressure-on-him-is-driven-by-elites-voters-paint-a-more-complicated-picture/articleshow/111652309.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111652309.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:49:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-says-pressure-on-him-is-driven-by-elites-voters-paint-a-more-complicated-picture/articleshow/111652309.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国暴雨造成四人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/four-killed-as-heavy-rains-pound-south-korea/articleshow/111651618.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111651618.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国的大雨造成四人死亡，基础设施和道路遭到严重破坏。 50个地区发布山体滑坡警报，导致3,500人被困。内政部长指出，严重程度很少见。悲惨的死亡包括被困在洪水地区并被溢出的溪流冲走的人。据报道，该国最近发生的洪水共有 44 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/four-killed-as-heavy-rains-pound-south-korea/articleshow/111651618.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国特别报告员：缅甸军政府“试图摧毁国家”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmar-junta-trying-to-destroy-country-un-special-rapporteur/articleshow/111652016.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111652016.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国缅甸特别报告员周四警告说，缅甸军政府似乎“试图摧毁一个它无法控制的国家”。 “军政府似乎正试图摧毁一个它无法控制的国家。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 05:38:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/myanmar-junta-trying-to-destroy-country-un-special-rapporteur/articleshow/111652016.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们正处于火灾年”：热浪引发美国西部各州令人震惊的野火激增</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/we-are-in-a-fire-year-heat-wave-sparks-alarming-wildfire-surge-in-western-states-of-us/articleshow/111650601.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111650601.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于持续的热浪、气温飙升和湿度骤降，西部各州正面临不断升级的野火危险。加州今年已处理了 3,500 多起野火，燃烧面积近 325 平方英里。俄勒冈州也面临严重火灾，而热浪影响了全美超过 1.42 亿人，打破了多项高温记录并造成多人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 04:52:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/we-are-in-a-fire-year-heat-wave-sparks-alarming-wildfire-surge-in-western-states-of-us/articleshow/111650601.cms</guid></item><item><title>纽约拍卖150岁剑龙骨架：售价多少？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/new-york-auction-to-sell-150-year-old-stegosaurus-skeleton-how-much-will-it-cost/articleshow/111649336.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111649336.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最大的剑龙骨架“Apex”将于纽约拍卖，这引起了古生物学家对将稀有发现出售给私人收藏家的担忧。它价值 4-600 万美元，被认为非常重要，但在科学界颇具争议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/new-york-auction-to-sell-150-year-old-stegosaurus-skeleton-how-much-will-it-cost/articleshow/111649336.cms</guid></item><item><title>“资金完全断绝了”：乔·拜登竞选团队面临筹款危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-money-has-absolutely-shut-off-joe-biden-campaign-faces-fundraising-crisis/articleshow/111649545.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111649545.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于在与特朗普的辩论中表现不佳，拜登竞选团队正在筹款方面陷入困境。捐款大幅减少，大笔捐款可能减少一半以上。辩论后的筹款激增很快就消散了，捐助者对此不以为然。此外，在要求拜登退出的呼声中，拜登对竞选的承诺存在不确定性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-money-has-absolutely-shut-off-joe-biden-campaign-faces-fundraising-crisis/articleshow/111649545.cms</guid></item><item><title>政治权力夫妇：克林顿助手胡玛·阿贝丁与乔治·索罗斯的儿子亚历克斯订婚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/political-power-couple-clinton-aide-huma-abedin-gets-engaged-to-george-soross-son-alex/articleshow/111649435.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111649435.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 03:41:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/political-power-couple-clinton-aide-huma-abedin-gets-engaged-to-george-soross-son-alex/articleshow/111649435.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普将于 7 月 27 日在比特币 2024 年会议上发表讲话</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-address-bitcoin-2024-conference-on-july-27/articleshow/111648508.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111648508.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-to-address-bitcoin-2024-conference-on-july-27/articleshow/111648508.cms</guid></item><item><title>2025 年计划：特朗普当选总统后重塑美国的计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/project-2025-inside-trumps-plan-to-reshape-america-if-he-wins-the-presidency/articleshow/111648390.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111648390.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Project 2025 重点关注一系列广泛的保守派优先事项，包括限制堕胎、减少 LGBTQ+ 权利、放弃解决气候变化和收入不平等问题的努力，以及对联邦政府劳动力实施彻底变革。该项目呼吁解雇数千名公务员、扩大总统权力、解散教育部门、实施减税、禁止色情制品、停止销售堕胎药等。然而，该文件因其可能破坏民主并导致政治暴力而受到批评。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:56:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/project-2025-inside-trumps-plan-to-reshape-america-if-he-wins-the-presidency/articleshow/111648390.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我不再袖手旁观”：特朗普的前妻玛拉·梅普尔斯“愿意”担任他的副总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/im-not-sitting-back-anymore-trumps-ex-wife-marla-maples-is-open-to-serve-him-as-his-vice-president/articleshow/111648513.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111648513.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的前妻玛拉·梅普尔斯 (Marla Maples) 表达了对他 2024 年总统竞选的支持，并愿意成为他的竞选搭档。在接受采访时，她强调，尽管特朗普存在法律问题，但她愿意更加直言不讳地支持特朗普。梅普尔斯淡化了特朗普的法律麻烦，坚称他是无辜的，并表示愿意以任何身份协助他的竞选活动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/im-not-sitting-back-anymore-trumps-ex-wife-marla-maples-is-open-to-serve-him-as-his-vice-president/articleshow/111648513.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国将部署“星球大战”激光武器对抗朝鲜无人机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-in-world-south-korea-to-deploy-starwars-laser-weapons-to-counter-north-korean-drones/articleshow/111648259.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111648259.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国将通过部署激光武器对抗朝鲜无人机来创造历史，成为第一个这样做的国家。 “星球大战项目”将采用具有成本效益的静音武器，能够精确击落无人机。由于朝韩双方继续违反停战协定，局势高度紧张，引发了人们对未来冲突的担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/first-in-world-south-korea-to-deploy-starwars-laser-weapons-to-counter-north-korean-drones/articleshow/111648259.cms</guid></item><item><title>“恐怖必须失败”：北约派遣F-16战机支持乌克兰新的支持行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/terror-must-fail-nato-sends-f-16-jets-to-bolster-ukraine-in-new-support-effort/articleshow/111647995.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111647995.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;北约盟国向乌克兰转让F-16战机，履行军事援助承诺。峰会承诺提供400亿欧元支持乌克兰。人们担心与俄罗斯可能发生冲突。盟国强调团结一致保卫北约领土。美国国务卿强调阻止俄罗斯侵略的重要性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 02:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/terror-must-fail-nato-sends-f-16-jets-to-bolster-ukraine-in-new-support-effort/articleshow/111647995.cms</guid></item><item><title>“它只会变得更好”：马斯克转向第二人称测试大脑技术</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/its-only-going-to-get-better-musk-moving-on-to-second-person-to-test-brain-tech/articleshow/111647525.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111647525.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由埃隆·马斯克领导的 Neuralink 正在推进脑机接口技术，并已转移到第二位患者身上。第一个肩膀以下瘫痪的病人诺兰·阿博（Noland Arbaugh）成功地用大脑控制了电脑光标。 Neuralink 解决了最初的问题，旨在植入更深的线程以实现更好的信号检测。马斯克设想未来的改进可以提供超人的能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 01:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/its-only-going-to-get-better-musk-moving-on-to-second-person-to-test-brain-tech/articleshow/111647525.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑新的防御战略来应对中国的产业政策</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-eyes-new-defensive-strategies-to-tackle-chinas-industrial-policies/articleshow/111647532.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111647532.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 01:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-eyes-new-defensive-strategies-to-tackle-chinas-industrial-policies/articleshow/111647532.cms</guid></item><item><title>在 23 名宣誓就职的德西议员中，3 人选择《薄伽梵歌》，1 人选择 Sundar Gutka，5 人选择《圣经》</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/out-of-23-desi-mps-to-swear-in-3-choose-bhagavad-gita-one-picks-sundar-gutka-five-opt-for-bible/articleshow/111642822.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111642822.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在英国议会，PIO 议员为他们的宣誓仪式选择了各种圣书和宣言。锡克教议员因依据圣经宣誓而面临争议。保守党议员同时以《钦定版圣经》和《薄伽梵歌》宣誓。工党议员选择宣誓而非宣誓。新议员介绍《薄伽梵歌》和《新约》。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 20:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/out-of-23-desi-mps-to-swear-in-3-choose-bhagavad-gita-one-picks-sundar-gutka-five-opt-for-bible/articleshow/111642822.cms</guid></item><item><title>Shockat Adam 活动家 Majid Freeman 在英国被指控犯有恐怖罪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/shockat-adam-campaigner-majid-freeman-charged-with-terror-offences-in-uk/articleshow/111642669.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111642669.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 19:43:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/shockat-adam-campaigner-majid-freeman-charged-with-terror-offences-in-uk/articleshow/111642669.cms</guid></item><item><title>滞留在太空：尽管波音公司的 Starliner 太空舱最近发生故障，美国宇航局宇航员仍对安全返回充满信心</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stranded-in-space-nasa-astronauts-confident-of-safe-return-despite-recent-failures-in-boeings-starliner-capsule/articleshow/111640414.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111640414.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;两名本应在几周前返回地球的宇航员周三表示，尽管出现了故障，但他们相信波音的太空舱能够安全地将他们送回地球。美国宇航局试飞员布奇·威尔莫尔（Butch Wilmore）和苏尼·威廉姆斯（Suni Williams）上月初登上波音公司的新型 Starliner 太空舱，成为第一批乘坐该太空舱的人。泄漏和推进器故障几乎使它们到达国际空间站的旅程脱轨，并且使它们在那里停留的时间比计划的要长得多。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:29:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/stranded-in-space-nasa-astronauts-confident-of-safe-return-despite-recent-failures-in-boeings-starliner-capsule/articleshow/111640414.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿联酋大规模审判：40多人因“恐怖”链接被判处终身监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-mass-trial-over-40-sentenced-to-life-in-prison-for-terror-links/articleshow/111640509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/111640509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:55:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-mass-trial-over-40-sentenced-to-life-in-prison-for-terror-links/articleshow/111640509.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>